const url = new URL("http://localhost/admin/payout-accounts/{id}");

let params = {
    "firstname": "Jon",
    "middlename": "M",
    "lastname": "Snow",
    "birthdate": "2021-05-06",
    "email": "jonsnow@gmail.com",
    "mobile": "09095123123",
    "address1": "B32 L7 North Kingslanding",
    "address2": "B32 L7 North Kingslanding",
    "address3": "B32 L7 North Kingslanding",
    "city": "Makati",
    "state": "",
    "country": "PH",
    "zip": "1306",
    "nationality": "Filipino",
    "nature_of_work": "Developer",
    "document.*.doc": ".V4x"RZtnCfa",
    "document.*.idnum": "0ivT"Ntoh<C+",
    "document.*.exp": "swCa|Sf5\IlK",
    "document.*.doc_proof_0": "$|?Ar+oH1MYd",
    "id": "5",
};

Object.keys(params).forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

let headers = {
    "Accept": "application/json",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
}

fetch(url, {
    method: "PUT",
    headers: headers,
})
    .then(response => response.json())
    .then(json => console.log(json));
